{"title":"路边　","authors":["柯炽"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":1,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"路边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柯炽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个车床，一个钻床，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把老虎钳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个师傅，一个徒弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修理站就设在十字路边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两张破帆权作瓦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踏大地，头顶青天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担子甚重非等闲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等着修的农具摆了一线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚钻过电机齿轮的钻头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接着给新式水泵打眼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那双沾满机油的巨手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又校正着一个个犁尖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅挥锤如龙腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徒弟掌钳也挺熟练；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修得又好又快还保用呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老农翘着拇指称赞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三星未退就开工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收工时天色都已晚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民个个点头笑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大哥和我们一样钟点！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}